{"title":"豆花开的时候","authors":["王雁伍"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":9,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"豆花开的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王雁伍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘您常在豆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘您常在青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草旁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那只又肥又壮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹦蹦跳跳的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄牛儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你那十个指头儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拔草把它喂大的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喂的它能耕田，拉车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛儿闪闪发亮光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘，你出嫁了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶上你那黄牛儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去走婆家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车上坐着你们俩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄牛拉车慢慢走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们小俩口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑嘻嘻的把话讲："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他对你说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“俺翻身分了五亩地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种上了二亩半棉花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓬蓬生生的大叶子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一棵棵都长的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么墩实。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，学着他的口气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我就喜欢墩墩实实的！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的脸红啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红的象个红柿子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你也知道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的小名叫“墩实”呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你低下了头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘴角儿咬着下衣巾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想笑，又有点儿羞臊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你俩的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟着小牛儿的铜铃铃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咯啷啷地颤动着……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这正是豆花儿开的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豆花儿香喷喷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香透了你小俩口儿的心！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九四九、八、一○"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}